{"type": "article", "id": 14629, "title": "切尔西说了几年的斯坦福桥新主场，第一次公布了球场模型", "description": "设计师说他们受了威斯敏斯特教堂哥特式风格的启发", "date": "2015-09-08T14:25:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 9822, "name": "切尔西"}, {"id": 15701, "name": "球场"}, {"id": 8320, "name": "Herzog & de Meuron"}], "category": 17, "author": 101857, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607132014OrbDLYlV32wRyBMP.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t自<span> 12 </span>年前俄罗斯富商罗曼·阿布拉莫维奇入主英超切尔西俱乐部以来，切尔西逐渐成为英超战绩最出色的球队。随着俱乐部越来越受欢迎，球队原主场斯坦福桥球场的容量愈发无法满足需求。上赛季，切尔西 <span><a href=\"http://www.itv.com/news/anglia/2015-07-17/norwich-city-had-highest-stadium-capacity-percentage-in-the-championship-survey-finds/\">99.82% <span>的主场上座率</span></a></span>是全英超最高的，但斯坦福桥球场却只有<span> 4.1 </span>万多个座位，远少于竞争对手如曼联和阿森纳的球场容量（<span><a href=\"http://www.espn.co.uk/football/chelsea/story/2593398/chelsea-unveil-stadium-model-of-new-stamford-bridge\"><span>约</span> 7.5 <span>万和</span> 6.0 <span>万座</span></a></span>）。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t切尔西和阿布在几年前就意识到这个问题，并启动了主场重建计划，要将斯坦福桥扩建成更大规模的球场，亦为俱乐部创造更多比赛日收入。他们委托瑞士建筑事务所 <span>Herzog &amp; de Meuron </span>来打造新球场。完工的<span><a href=\"http://www.espnfc.com/chelsea/story/2593398/chelsea-unveil-stadium-model-of-new-stamford-bridge\"><span>新球场将有</span><span>三层看台，座位<span>增至</span></span> 6 <span>万个，<span>造价<span>达</span></span></span> 5 <span>亿英镑（<span>全为<span>阿布本人<span>投资<span>）<span>。</span></span></span></span></span></span></a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t最近，切尔西球迷们终于可以看到新主场的样子了。俱乐部在斯坦福桥球场展出新球场的模型，也透露了以前从未公开过的设计细节。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071320103oe9xu4iAbUEYKO2.jpg\" title=\"上图为现球场，下图为新球场模型\" alt=\"上图为现球场，下图为新球场模型\" data-ratio=\"1.66435185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>上图为现球场，下图为新球场模型</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132010iB4olpzydNfhA6q2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">外立面\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132011GXpNVoa8BHzl7D2j.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56466877\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071320115iz6NOuKZ81qWSnG.jpg\" title=\"球场周边环境\" alt=\"球场周边环境\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>球场周边环境</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132012lkCHvEqKU87fiGBZ.jpg\" title=\"球场内部\" alt=\"球场内部\" data-ratio=\"0.66561514\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>球场内部</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132012bs9SPCG8vQ2iJkTz.jpg\" title=\"屋顶\" alt=\"屋顶\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>屋顶</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这些模型第一次完整呈现了斯坦福桥未来的模样。球场整体为不规则廓形。一系列细长的混凝土砖柱和拱廊包裹着它，作为球场的外骨骼。细柱向上延伸到最高处，形成一个圆，而后又向下“折叠”形成比足球场面积稍大的长方形开口，这就是球场的屋顶了。<a href=\"http://E:/%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C/%E5%A5%BD%E5%A5%87%E5%BF%83%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5/%E5%88%87%E5%B0%94%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B0%E7%90%83%E5%9C%BA%20%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/The%20stadium%20will%20be%20wrapped%20in%20a%20cage%20of%20slender%20concrete%20and%20brick%20columns%20that%20will%20rise%20to%20a%20zig-zagging%20profile,%20before%20folding%20over%20to%20form%20the%20roof%20%E2%80%93%20as%20if%20the%20architects%E2%80%99%20tangle%20of%20struts%20in%20Beijing%E2%80%99s%20Bird%E2%80%99s%20Nest%20stadium%20had%20been%20straightened%20out%20an\">用《卫报》的话说</a>，“它就像北京鸟巢体育馆的骨架被梳理整齐了”。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t而<span><a href=\"http://www.bdonline.co.uk/5077404.article\"><span>设计师则<span>表示</span></span></a></span>这是受了威斯敏斯特大教堂柱子、扶壁及其整体哥特式建筑风格的启发。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t由于原址在富勒姆路的斯坦福桥球场毗邻铁路和地铁，周围有住宅区，所以球场的改造还需对周边社区建筑进行改建。比如说，球场边上的两个酒店都会被移除，在此基础上，四个看台将下沉并且外扩；原先的铁路线上方将建人行道，便于周边居民通行。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t而据原先公布的效果图，这里还会建起一座连接球场和附近<span> Fulham Broadway </span>地铁站的桥，球迷们可以直接从地铁站走过来。桥拱下有一系列酒吧、咖啡馆和商店，供来看球的球迷休闲娱乐。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132012wKIlE9gd2O1rbmo5.jpg\" title=\"新建起的桥\" alt=\"新建起的桥\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>新建起的桥</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071320132YDlm4y7AsRXMzbN.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132014sYQoD5GRUqB2cKvu.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">于 7 月公布的球场效果图\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t如果改建计划顺利进行，那么<span> 2016/2017 </span>赛季将是切尔西在现主场比赛的最后一个赛季，那之后他们可能会租用温布利球场，直到<span> 2020 </span>年新斯坦福桥正式开放。但伦敦的另一支英超球队热刺也在建新球场，也希望租下温布利，所以双方主场（扩）建时比赛要在哪里进行，这些还未最终确定。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t图片来源：<span><a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3217477/Chelsea-fans-look-new-home-club-unveil-model-Stamford-Bridge.html\">dailymai</a>l</span>，<span><a href=\"http://cdn.fansided.com/wp-content/blogs.dir/229/files/2014/06/olympic-preview-london-city-views2-850x560.jpg\">fanside</a></span>，<span><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/architecture-design-blog/2015/jul/03/chelseas-new-stadium-inspired-medieval-village-beyond-ugliness-roman-abramovich#img-1\">theguardian</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}